34
00:02:49,130 --> 00:02:56,010
Hong Kong’s laissez-faire capitalism,
is often described as stateless capitalism.

35
00:02:56,010 --> 00:03:00,760
The Hong Kong government has an explicit policy
of “positive non-intervention”:

36
00:03:00,760 --> 00:03:04,480
Don’t interfere with the market.

37
00:03:04,480 --> 00:03:09,660
Albeit subtle and indirect,
Hong Kong’s economic development reveals

38
00:03:09,660 --> 00:03:16,650
