since the 1950s.

40
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:23,370
For example,
the government owns all urban land.

41
00:03:23,370 --> 00:03:28,840
The land is leased in a land market entirely
controlled by government.

42
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:34,810
This land regime not only helps the government
to obtain substantial public revenue,

43
00:03:34,810 --> 00:03:42,729
